				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$N=1$$\end{document}N=1 for consistency with what follows), meaning we only need to track the dynamics of S and I densities, given by the following ordinary differential equations,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
