In general, the pair approximation appears to be a good ‘average’ of the results from the stochastic mode since it is always within the maximum/minimum bounds and regularly within the IQRs. The ‘fit’ appears to be least good as L approaches 1, as would be expected. The pair approximation is less accurate for \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
